I have a 25 million dollar plot in Prague, an apartment worth 10 million dollars, another apartment worth 8 million dollars, a collection of artwork worth about 10 million dollars, an Aston Martin worth 3.5 million dollars and a Škoda Superb worth 1 million dollars and a few million dollars on my account.
